title: Sjukan
overview: In the Hospital's department for undetermined stomach and heart diseases, there are three patients who seem to be enjoying themselves rudely, miscellaneous worker Bert Hersby, Östermalm resident Rutger Ahlenius and mother pig Patrik Larsson. They are cared for with a firm hand by the slightly distracted Dr. Söderberg and nurse Nader, who insists on calling all patients "Svenne".
